Set the controller type to XBOX360:confopts_ph.sh -p set -a Ctrls -o PH_CTRL_TYPE='XBOX360'
View help on how to configure a usb XBOX360 controller on your system:confctrl_ph.sh -p help -c usb -t XBOX360
View help on how to configure a wireless XBOX360 controller on your system:confctrl_ph.sh -p help -c wireless -t XBOX360
Return to previous menu:return
